**STRUKTUR YANG DIINGINKAN:**

src/
├── components/
│   ├── common/ (Reusable UI: Navbar, Button, Card)
│   ├── layout/ (Layout wrappers)
│   └── features/ (Feature-specific components)
├── pages/ (Page-level components/views)
├── features/ (Feature-based modules)
│   ├── auth/ (components, hooks, services)
│   ├── soal/ (components, hooks, services)
│   ├── tryout/ (components, hooks, services)
│   ├── ai/ (components, hooks, services)
│   └── vocab/ (components, hooks, services)
├── services/ (API, Firebase, external services)
│   ├── firebase/
│   ├── api/
│   └── vercel/
├── utils/ (Helper functions)
├── hooks/ (Custom React hooks global)
├── context/ (State management)
├── constants/ (Config, routes, constants)
└── styles/ (Global CSS)

